author: bentmann
msg: [MINVOKER-64] invoker:install does not install dependencies unless they are in the reactor

author: jukka
msg: We only include ant.jar (from Apache Ant 1.6.2) as a dependency for the PDFToTextTask class. This dependency is fully under ALv2 and has no extra attribution requirements. Thus we can drop the W3C, SAX, and ALv1 licenses that full Apache Ant distributions contain to cover the included XML libraries.

author: markt
msg: Update auto generated files as a result of ELParser.jjt change

I have not re-instated the AL2 header in the auto-generated files. On reflection I don't think it makes sense for auto-generated files and the file they are generated from has the AL2 header. It also makes re-generating the files simpler.
